page.title: 12MY HOUSE
page.content: {My House} My name is Lisa Myson. I live at 25, Wembley Ave.Maylandsea.My mum and dad have lived here ever since they were married,17 years ago. I have two sisters called Paula and Mechelle.I live in a semi-detached house made out of bricks.My house has three bedrooms,two bathrooms and one dining room,one sitting room and a kitchen.In the living room we have the telephone and a video.When my dad moved here he had the dining room and a bathroom built on.My garden is quite small and it has five trees in it.We have two plum trees,one cherry tree one apple tree and one pear tree.We have not got many flowers but I have an evergreen bush and I also live near the sea.
